.name
MouseXY
.type
Display Tool
.short
Displays mouse coordinates.
.description
A small utility that shows the mouse coordinates and the
color at that position.  It can be moved from screen to
screen (automatically evacuates any closing screen).  Is
able to show coordinates even when you are moving/resizing
windows or moving Workbench icons.  This is version 1.1,
an update to version 1.0 on disk 483.
